    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 1 requirements for Class II devices at MRL 2. CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the CPB device. Relative hemolysis index predictions satisfy RH < 1 acceptance criterion across all five operating conditions. Assessment team accepts the simulation results as credible evidence for the intended regulatory submission.",
